@page "/policy"
@rendermode InteractiveServer

<PageTitle>Policy</PageTitle>

<div class="policy-container">

    <h1>Adoption Policy</h1>

    <div class="policy-item">
        <h2>Welcome to Pawfect Match</h2>
        <p>
            Thank you for considering adopting a dog from Pawfect! Our mission is to connect wonderful dogs with loving homes. Below you’ll find our adoption policy, designed to ensure the safety and well-being of our dogs while facilitating a smooth adoption process.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-item">
        <h2>Eligibility</h2>
        <p>
            To adopt a dog, you must meet the following requirements:<br />
            - You must be at least 18 years old.<br />
            - You must have a stable and safe living environment.<br />
            - All current pets must be spayed/neutered and up-to-date on vaccinations.<br />
            - Adoption fees are required and vary based on the dog’s age and breed.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-item">
        <h2>Adoption Process</h2>
        <p>
            Our adoption process involves the following steps:<br />
            1. Complete an adoption application.<br />
            2. Meet with an adoption counselor for an interview.<br />
            3. Complete a home visit if applicable.<br />
            4. Pay the adoption fee and finalize the adoption.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-item">
        <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
        <p>
            We are committed to providing a safe and loving environment for every dog in our care. Once you adopt a dog, you become part of the Pawfect family, and we are here to support you throughout your journey together.
        </p>
        <p>
            If you have any questions, please feel free to <a href="/contact" class="policy-link">Contact Us</a>.
        </p>
    </div>

</div>

